<br>
0725 Marzin's Mark 575 1 hour 23 minutes<br>
0470 PoTG 1200 1 hour 40 minutes<br>
0430 Khura's Focusing 1250<br>
0225 Brell's Mountainous Barrier 200<br>
HP: 1850<br>
Cost: 3 Peridots, 3225 Mana Single Group, or 6050 MGB + 200 per group<br>
<br>
1150 Blessing of Aego 2000 2 hours 30 minutes<br>
0430 Khura's Focusing 1250<br>
0225 Brell's Mountainous Barrier 200<br>
HP: 1805<br>
Cost: 4 Peridots 3450 Mana Single Group, or 6500 MGB + 200 per group<br>
<br>
1300 Ancient: Gift of Aegolism 2000<br>
0430 Khura's Focusing 1250<br>
0225 Brell's Mountainous Barrier 200<br>
HP: 1955<br>
